The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation
		 Monday, August 23, 2004 				 NCP recruit
																								Aurangabad, Aug. 22 (PTI): Actor Parikshit Sahni today joined the Sharad Pawar-led Nationalist Congress Party. Clad in white kurta-pyjama and  a black jacket, the veteran Bollywood actors aid he had  been searching for an ideal political party for the last  two decades and his search ended with the NCP. I feel that  I am at an appropriate place at an appropriate time, Sahni  said. 
